items.title: Awesome Streaming
items.content_text:
### Table of Contents / Online Machine Learning

*   [streamDM (‚≠ê495)](https://github.com/huawei-noah/streamDM) \[Scala] - mining Big Data streams using Spark Streaming from Huawei.
*   [StormCV (‚≠ê170)](https://github.com/sensorstorm/StormCV) \[Java] - enables the use of Apache Storm for video processing by adding computer vision (CV) specific operations and data model.
*   [trident-ml (‚≠ê382)](https://github.com/pmerienne/trident-ml) \[Java] - realtime online machine learning library based on Trident.
*   [yurita (‚≠ê108)](https://github.com/paypal/yurita) \[Scala] - Anomaly detection framework built on Spark Structured Streaming from Paypal.
items.content_html:
Table of Contents / Online Machine Learning

  • streamDM (‚≠ê495) [Scala] - mining Big Data streams using Spark Streaming from Huawei.
  • StormCV (‚≠ê170) [Java] - enables the use of Apache Storm for video processing by adding computer vision (CV) specific operations and data model.
  • trident-ml (‚≠ê382) [Java] - realtime online machine learning library based on Trident.
  • yurita (‚≠ê108) [Scala] - Anomaly detection framework built on Spark Structured Streaming from Paypal.
